OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1772193824
OL,3,CMet Police officer who ran coffee
OL,4,Cbusiness whilst suspended on full pay
OL,5,Csacked
OL,7,FA Metropolitan Police officer who ran
OL,8,Fa coffee business whilst suspended on
OL,9,Ffull pay has been sacked.
OL,11,FPc Stanley Kennett applied for a
OL,12,Fbusiness interest called The Coffee
OL,13,FCycle, in West Sussex, whilst
OL,14,Fsuspended from duty on 23rd April 2024
OL,15,Fand was notified that it had been
OL,16,Fdeclined a week later, according to a
OL,17,Ftribunal ruling.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
