OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1772193824
OL,3,CMet Police officer who ran coffee
OL,4,Cbusiness whilst suspended on full pay
OL,5,Csacked
OL,7,FIn September 2025, it was confirmed
OL,8,Fthat the 31-year-old "continued to
OL,9,Fengage in and operate this
OL,10,Funauthorised business interest" whilst
OL,11,Freceiving full pay from the force, the
OL,12,Fruling said.
OL,14,FFollowing a misconduct hearing on
OL,15,FFebruary 12, Mr Kennett was found to
OL,16,Fhave breached police standards of
OL,17,Fprofessional behaviour amounting to
OL,18,Fgross misconduct and was dismissed
OL,19,Fwithout notice.
OL,26,@pD@VOUrD@_O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
