OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1772193824
OL,3,CMet Police officer who ran coffee
OL,4,Cbusiness whilst suspended on full pay
OL,5,Csacked
OL,7,FThe Coffee Cycle is listed as having
OL,8,Fbeen incorporated on April 1 2025,
OL,9,Fwith Mr Kennett listed as the director
OL,10,Fon Companies House.
OL,12,FThe business, based in a bike shop in
OL,13,FStorrington, West Sussex, serves
OL,14,Fcoffee, cake and pastries and provides
OL,15,Fcatering for events, according to its
OL,16,Fwebsite and social media.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1772193824
OL,3,CMet Police officer who ran coffee
OL,4,Cbusiness whilst suspended on full pay
OL,5,Csacked
OL,7,FIn the ruling, commander Andy Brittain
OL,8,Fsaid of the venture: "This was not
OL,9,Fsimply a volunteering opportunity,
OL,10,Fthis was a full-blown and expanding
OL,11,Fbusiness supported by incorporation of
OL,12,Fthat business, the granting of a
OL,13,Fdirector's loan and employment of
OL,14,Fstaff.
OL,16,F"Pc Kennett is also noted to have been
OL,17,Factively engaged on social media
OL,18,Fpromoting that business.
OL,26,@pD@VOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1772193824
OL,3,CMet Police officer who ran coffee
OL,4,Cbusiness whilst suspended on full pay
OL,5,Csacked
OL,7,F"This was a sophisticated operation,
OL,8,Fand Pc Kennett appears heavily
OL,9,Finvolved at all points.
OL,11,F"All of which appears to undermine the
OL,12,Fsubmission on his behalf that at
OL,13,Frelevant points he lacked capacity to
OL,14,Funderstand the significance of the
OL,15,Fconsequences of his actions."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUwD@]O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
