OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1772193824
OL,3,CMet Police officer who ran coffee
OL,4,Cbusiness whilst suspended on full pay
OL,5,Csacked
OL,7,FMr Brittain said: "Running a business,
OL,8,Fwhether for financial gain or not,
OL,9,Fwhilst suspended on full pay, brings
OL,10,Fpolicing and the MPS (Metropolitan
OL,11,FPolice Service) in particular into
OL,12,Fdisrepute.
OL,14,F"Members of the public would not
OL,15,Fexpect serving police officers to act
OL,16,Fin this way."
OL,18,FAccording to the ruling, Pc Kennett
OL,19,Fadmitted his actions but accepted that
OL,20,Fthey amounted to misconduct only.
OL,26,@oD@SOUvD@AOUxD@MOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
