PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1772193824
OL,3,CMet Police officer who ran coffee
OL,4,Cbusiness whilst suspended on full pay
OL,5,Csacked
OL,7,FThe former officer, who had been
OL,8,Fsuspended from duty on full pay since
OL,9,FOctober 2023, was also placed on the
OL,10,FCollege of Policing's barred list.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/7
